Introducing…
The Top Secret Event Space!
If you’re looking for an intimate venue with a great location and modern vibe, our new event space is just the spot for
Located right next to our sister venue, The Wooly, in downtown Gainesville lies The Top Secret Event Space. This private room is perfect for seated dinners up to 40 guests, or can hold up to 50 guests for cocktail-style events.

Sunday, March 9th
Days N Daze
Local News Legend
Confession Kids
Doors 7pm / Show 8pm
$23
Formed in 2008, Days N Daze hail from Houston and have performed worldwide, most recently with music released by Fat Wreck Chords. 2020's Billboard-charter Show Me the Blueprints introduced many to "thrashgrass," DND's acoustic punk addressing issues like mental health and addiction, but also buoyant with the ideas of family and hope.
Local News Legend join the tour with gentle yet fierce folk punk tunes from Pennsylvania.
Local GNV darlings Confession Kid open the night with their Florida folk punk.
18+
All tickets non-refundable unless the show is cancelled.

Sunday, March 9th
Days N Daze
Local News Legend
Confession Kids
Doors 7pm / Show 8pm
$23
Formed in 2008, Days N Daze hail from Houston and have performed worldwide, most recently with music released by Fat Wreck Chords. 2020's Billboard-charter Show Me the Blueprints introduced many to "thrashgrass," DND's acoustic punk addressing issues like mental health and addiction, but also buoyant with the ideas of family and hope.
Local News Legend join the tour with gentle yet fierce folk punk tunes from Pennsylvania.
Local GNV darlings Confession Kid open the night with their Florida folk punk.
18+
All tickets non-refundable unless the show is cancelled.

Formed in 2008, Days N Daze hail from Houston and have performed worldwide, most recently with music released by Fat Wreck Chords. 2020's Billboard-charter Show Me the Blueprints introduced many to "thrashgrass," DND's acoustic punk addressing issues like mental health and addiction, but also buoyant with the ideas of family and hope.
Local News Legend join the tour with gentle yet fierce folk punk tunes from Pennsylvania.
Local GNV darlings Confession Kid open the night with their Florida folk punk.
